      • open

        public void open()
        This method opens the can if it is closed. Remains open if it was already opened.

      • sip

        public int sip()
        This method decreases the amount of soda can by 10cc if the can was opened. If the amount of soda in the can is less than 10, then there will be no soda left.
        Returns:
        Returns the amount of soda that was taken out of the can.

      • gulp

        public int gulp()
        This method decreases the amount of soda can by 50cc if the can was opened. If the amount of soda in the can is less than 50, then there will be no soda left.
        Returns:
        Returns the amount of soda that was taken out of the can.
